    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require substantial mechanical and cosmetic work. The engine currently runs but struggles with a rough idle and occasional stalling, and the transmission exhibits a noticeable delay when shifting gears. Externally, there is significant rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with various dents and faded paint. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional air conditioning system. This car is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a dedicated restoration project.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
