      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in pristine condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014not a scratch or a smudge to be found. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh car smell. If you want a top-tier vehicle that's been loved and cared for, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
