      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This example is mechanically flawless, with the critical rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement already completed. The double-VANOS system has been overhauled for peak variable valve timing precision. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, retaining its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior bolsters reflect climate-controlled storage. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist.",
